This is pretty much a clone of the original CSS. It makes some adjustments to better suit sites where it will be crammed into a smaller space.

Chat area is larger, roster is smaller and the usersname will appear over the the date as opposed to being adjacent.

Two new images for room owner and moderators as seen in Adium.im

Place the following in your head, after the default.css


<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="PATH-TO/simples/simples.css" />

Naturally you need to replace the "PATH-TO" with your path.

Tested in Chrome, Firefox, Opera and Safari on Lion (Apple Mac). Not had any other complaints from users yet.

